1
00:01:23,879 --> 00:01:25,120
What do you want to do?

2
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,640
Tell me now,

3
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,799
why did I have to hear about your departure

4
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:30,959
from someone else?

5
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:33,599
It happened suddenly,

6
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,599
I didn't have time to tell you.

7
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,280
Is your phone just for show?

8
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,719
I'm sorry.

9
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,799
Do you think your apology is worth something?

10
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,439
Don't you like photography?

11
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,959
The SP Award

12
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,560
will be a great help to you

13
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,319
in the future.

14
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,959
Do you think if it weren't for you,

15
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,920
they would see my work?

16
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,799
Gold will shine anywhere.

17
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,400
Your first goal now

18
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,680
is to go abroad and win awards,

19
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,080
then come back and study hard.

20
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:11,919
Jiang Yue,

21
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,639
I'm asking you seriously now,

22
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,360
do you like me or not?

23
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:52,879
No.

24
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,800
Say it again.

25
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,639
No.

26
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,439
I'll say it ten times if I have to.

27
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,080
You don't attract me at all.

28
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,520
I just don't like you.

29
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,039
Don't you know yourself at all?

30
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,520
I said I don't like you.

31
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:27,639
I'm sorry.

32
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:29,919
I'm sorry.

33
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,120
I...

34
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,280
We're even.

35
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,280
Study hard.

36
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:44,639
I...

37
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:50,240
I'm leaving.

38
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:45,800
Jiang Yue,

39
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,600
do you know how sad you made me?

40
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:53,959
And I

41
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,000
won't let you go.

42
00:05:01,319 --> 00:05:02,360
I'm going to punish you.

43
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,639
You're playing with fire.

44
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,839
Don't you like flirting?

45
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:26,839
I like it too.

46
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,759
I'm just playing by your rules,

47
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:56,600
and giving you a taste of your own medicine.

48
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:01,199
Jiang Yue, you really can't handle punishment.

49
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:37,680
This trick really works.

50
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,040
Auntie,

51
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,319
do you know where Qi went?

52
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,720
She has a flight at eleven o'clock tonight.

53
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,519
She said she was going abroad

54
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,480
to buy some things she needs.

55
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:24,399
Didn't you go with her?

56
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:26,879
I see.

57
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,879
Is Qi here?

58
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,399
She went to Chengyue Mall

59
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,800
with Chu Mo.

60
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,519
They seem to be having fun.

61
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,360
Do you like the clothes I bought?

62
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:52,519
Yeah, they look good.

63
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,600
Mr. Chu, let's go.

64
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,759
I have something to tell you.

65
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,120
Go ahead.

66
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,040
Alone.

67
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,160
I don't have time to talk to you alone.

68
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,279
Jiang Yue

69
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:08,920
You shouldn't be here.

70
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:09,759
Get out.

71
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:11,560
You've said a lot in such a short time.

72
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,240
So you chose him in the end, right?

73
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,240
Does it have anything to do with you?

74
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,639
What about last night?

75
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,720
My punishment for you.

76
00:08:23,079 --> 00:08:24,120
Do you punish everyone like this?

77
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:25,800
Not exactly.

78
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,480
It's just more than you think.

79
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,720
Are you just acting?

80
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,480
Have you ever seen me act like this to anyone else?

81
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,240
The evening ticket has been canceled.

82
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,480
Book it again when you go abroad.

83
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,000
How many?

84
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:45,720
Two.

85
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:00,519
Father,

86
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,679
it's the 24th today.

87
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,559
You should go to work.

88
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,279
I know.

89
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,360
He must be hiding something from me.

90
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,399
Good, good, good.

91
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,879
There's a surprise.

92
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,759
Yes.

93
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,120
Tell me the encryption key of Jiang Changfa.

94
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,360
You only have five seconds.

95
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,039
Jiang Changfa

96
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,879
is a loser under my command.

97
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,000
Only I can destroy him.

98
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:14,519
Okay?

99
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,480
Jiang Yue should be up by now.

100
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,240
I'll be out for a while.

101
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,720
Shen Yu will protect you.

102
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,200
Jiang Yue.

103
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:10,200
Sit.

104
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:20,320
I did want to use you against 3Z.

105
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,639
But you used me yesterday

106
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,559
to make Jiang Yue jealous.

107
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:25,440
We're even.

108
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,960
I understand. I won't push my luck.

109
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:31,480
But I'm here today

110
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,240
to ask you

111
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,360
if you know where Jiang Yue went.

112
00:11:34,879 --> 00:11:35,919
Why do you think

113
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:37,399
I know where he went?

114
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,840
Jiang Yue has subordinates,

115
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:43,759
but no friends.

116
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,799
I mean, before I met you.

117
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,399
I asked his subordinates,

118
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:50,840
but they wouldn't tell me.

119
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,200
So,

120
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,960
I had to ask you, his friend.

121
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:59,039
You do know some social rules.

122
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,120
But I really don't know where he went.

123
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,399
Lu Qi,

124
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,360
if Jiang Yue didn't tell you,

125
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,919
don't ask anything.

126
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,240
Just stay put, that's the best thing.

127
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,720
Do you know something?

128
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,320
If you know something,

129
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:18,919
just tell me.

130
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,840
I won't cause any trouble.

131
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,639
What is this?

132
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:52,720
Dark Web.

133
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,159
Dark Web?
